{"tid":2089511,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸妹真係好崇洋，啱啱佢問我係咪有bno","createTime":"2020-07-01T16:57:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T00:34:24.000Z","uid":27616,"like":28,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"df67de6f0b1a61f3eddad62bac315e42b974ae79","tid":2089511,"uid":27616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T16:57:27.000Z","msg":"以前溝過佢，好耐冇聯絡，突然間send嚟問<br />\n我心諗:我係帶都唔會帶你過去啦，我當你雞嚟咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bff5b62b30de3f9e68c54943145930417af818a","tid":2089511,"uid":200135,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T16:58:38.000Z","msg":"中出即飛啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe562f64b9d4b1a4e389234fc01c3e15f88a2d20","tid":2089511,"uid":147916,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T17:11:36.000Z","msg":"屌咗先啦"},{"pid":"9a5c0603e0eb9b483f5a0e3893ca1e6e265e6794","tid":2089511,"uid":15605,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T17:34:10.000Z","msg":"屌完一腳伸落床"},{"pid":"60cd81eb72a7e922cc10945c8e5df35e592a614d","tid":2089511,"uid":34140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T17:36:46.000Z","msg":"一答有就捉你架啦"},{"pid":"11225f216157b6490bd9ae591ea769d5948e81d0","tid":2089511,"uid":261914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T17:40:50.000Z","msg":"話有啦，睇下佢咩反應有咩講，然後開心share<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33541975202bd6f9bcfc6162e671453871ebc6e9","tid":2089511,"uid":156936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T18:03:12.000Z","msg":"lm睇故"},{"pid":"37a548af6553fb557af107a8313c571eb63cb466","tid":2089511,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T18:06:09.000Z","msg":"借個位，BNO平權正視聽<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑色五毛分化警告，大量五毛正在用藍絲有BNO、走人對唔住97後割97後等風向進行分化</span></span></strong>，大家小心。<br />\n<br />\n1.<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家比人拉過/有小朋友（細路是重點，香港未來棟樑，正如今時今日d前線義士，咪比佢地洗腦變小糞紅，否則香港係真正玩完）的話就應該即刻走</span></span></strong>，其他人亦應該起碼做好隨時走既準備，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">香港抗爭運動已經由本土抗爭升級為準國際戰爭， 我們能做的十分有限。 相反大家離開或準備好隨時可以離開，則美國及其盟友可以隨時採取行動，對香港進行制裁，令香港達至零經濟活動，攬炒香港經濟， 甚至日後作出軍事行動亦無需擔心誤傷香港人。</span></span></strong> 而且大家亦可用移民理由提取所有資產及強積金進一步<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">打擊香港的財政儲備</span></span></strong>。<br />\n而且多人走亦可以起到掩護最需要走既手足，救奶左野手足係目前最重要既事。<br />\n<br />\n2.大家<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無需擔心藍絲以及黑警移民英國</span></span></strong>，藍絲得兩種a.垃圾b.收成期，a.涯唔到六年移民監b.揾錢唔捨得走/走要承受巨大損失<br />\n<br />\n重點：大家<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不應該反對平權或推到現階段設立篩選，因為這樣會妨礙奶左野手足逃難</span></span></strong>。反而，大家應該在藍絲移民英國後再篤灰。大家，要記住，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">篤灰係一把藍絲頭上既利劍，一日未入籍一日都嚮度，我就係要佢地嚮英國每一日都擔心比人篤灰，呢樣恐懼做為懲罰先係最大懲罰</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n3.<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">97後手足唔會被割</span></span></strong>，首先，佢地可以跟BNO父母及配偶前往英國。第二，對於<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">未受BNO平權保障嘅人佢哋仲有美國既救生艇計劃</span></span></strong>，該計劃估計幾日內亦會通過。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">希望樓主可以pin，一齊擊退五毛</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"fa1694c0409a6853e70729a497cd8bb393b35a49","tid":2089511,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T18:40:18.000Z","msg":"有BNO未又係毒撚<br />\n去到大英帝國同鬼仔爭女"},{"pid":"860536039321650af3c3f74d0858675d27d551fc","tid":2089511,"uid":271130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T18:41:25.000Z","msg":"心態正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e10d23a9af46c8a54bec30dcb95a27422318a3e","tid":2089511,"uid":183601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T19:02:25.000Z","msg":"由今日開始<br />\n支那女人唔再target公屋, 會target bno"},{"pid":"8081caa563b76f99970c1f0bd27c6a8ecb442288","tid":2089511,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T19:21:11.000Z","msg":"講到明個dependants要usually live im Hong Kong<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ae4b83464d49685730f9af76604c3c07c52ca43","tid":2089511,"uid":222238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df67de6f0b1a61f3eddad62bac315e42b974ae79","tid":2089511,"uid":27616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T16:57:27.000Z","msg":"以前溝過佢，好耐冇聯絡，突然間send嚟問<br />\n我心諗:我係帶都唔會帶你過去啦，我當你雞嚟咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T22:03:12.000Z","msg":"點解要心諗?"},{"pid":"ad1466651ba332346020f07accf8c380c2077ca8","tid":2089511,"uid":222238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2bff5b62b30de3f9e68c54943145930417af818a","tid":2089511,"uid":200135,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T16:58:38.000Z","msg":"中出即飛啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T22:04:08.000Z","msg":"小心武漢肺炎"},{"pid":"1c1d50b2bc08e8aa8222c77f3a93ed29aea221a2","tid":2089511,"uid":61084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T22:08:20.000Z","msg":"直接大聲屌 ! 關你撚事呀臭雞!"},{"pid":"ff981716814f4d147b1201476c313267bb32991d","tid":2089511,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df67de6f0b1a61f3eddad62bac315e42b974ae79","tid":2089511,"uid":27616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T16:57:27.